item.title: Soufflé Pancakes - Hanabusa Café - Chicago, IL
item.author: Nathan Petersen
item.description: Custard soufflé pancakes with crème brûlée topping from Hanabusa Cafe in downtown Chicago, IL." Custard soufflé pancakes with crème brûlée topping from Hanabusa Cafe in downtown Chicago, IL. Fluffy like a cloud, tastes like heaven. Where? Hanabusa Cafe (hanabusacafechicago.com), located in downtown Chicago, IL, is a modern cafe which specializes in authentic Japanese soufflé pancakes. Soufflé Pancakes Hanabusa Cafe serves both traditional lunch food (e.g., rice bowl, ramen, etc) and brunch items.
